id: pm-g2zz
title: "As an agent in a million-item workspace, pm context and pm next give me a correct working set in under a second and a bounded token budget, without me knowing how big the workspace is"
description: "Agent story for the scale-out initiative (per capability-epic agent-story convention, changelog-excluded). Defines the experience bar the pm-9rxu children must jointly clear."
