acceptance_criteria: "On the synthetic 1M-item workspace: a fresh agent session can bootstrap (context -> next -> get -> claim) with every response sub-second and under the documented token budget; truncated views always say how to page deeper; no command requires the agent to adjust flags for workspace size"
