  "2026-07-22T18:26:38.641Z",codex-root,"Relationship rationale: million-item acceptance combines index latency, contention throughput, graph/property conformance, adaptive token packing, memory tiers, and the existing synthetic benchmark. Passing only one dimension cannot close the story."
